values: so yeah its been a long as time since i have wrote in here, maybe now that i'm done with school i'll have more time...well heres the latest news with me...i'm finally 18!!!!! yay!!! lol...i got a tattoo on my ass, its a star, and i just got my belly button pierced (top and bottom) a couple days ago...yeah the bottom one hurt so bad!!! i couldn't believe how bad it hurt! but its all good...its really cute...lol...and i'm finally outta high school, i graduate on wednesday! yay!!! and i finally got a job! you'll never guess where i work...wal-mart...lol...but hey i get paid pretty good! so its not that bad...its actually a pretty kewl place to work...although it does get boring at times...lol...but thats pretty much whats been going on in my life...pretty boring...but then exciting...lol...have a goodnight...laterness

if u haven't seen underworld yet i highly recomend that u find a way to see it!!!! it is a great movie!!! but i'm gonna go...have fun...lol...laterness

hey! been a while since i've wrote in here...lol...i've just been really busy! i've had a great week! lol...lets see, lets recall the past week...monday: went out with amber to mcdonalds and talked to some of my friends that i haven't talked to in a while and got to see destiny, best friends niece! shes so cute!!, tuesday: went out with amber again and talked to some more people that i haven't talked to in a while, like "j" (not gonna say names) this one kid almost lite mcdonalds on fire....lol...but he didn't thank god!, wednesday, went to mcdonalds with amber, and ended up going to "a" house and getting trashed with amber,  "a", "js", "b", "k", and "o", thursday: got trashed again with a lot of people...lol, friday: got buzzed, hooked up with "j" ("js" and "j" r 2 diff. ppl) and then went and spent the night at ambers...omg let me tell u about that, on the way to her house, down by pizza hut, 3 cops pull me over bc i my taillight was out...omg that really takes 3 cops...lol...but then they tried telling me that i was going 50 in a 30...yeah right! i was going about 35, and like amber was going faster then me...she was doing about 40, but freakin 3 of them pull me over and not one pulls her over...yeah lets do the math here...if i was really doing 50 and she was going faster than me don't u think one of them coulda gone after her? but hey i cant complain, they didn't write me a ticket! instead the cop that was talkin to me lied for me and said that i was on my way home from work! i was so grateful of that! and really happy bc i woulda got in some major trouble if i was to get a ticket! but yeah anyways on with the rest of my weekend...saturday i stayed home and slept bc no one wanted to come pick me up...sunday...left with amber, "a", and "j", and went over to "a" house and played some uno and then amber left and me "j" and "a" went to the huddle house...that was so funny...it was great! and then we went back to "a" house and then me and "j" came back to my house and yeah he didn't leave till 5 a.m. and i didn't get to sleep till like 5:30 only to be back up at 6:30 to go to school...monday...slept all day at school...lol..came home from school, and took a nap and then my aunt came down from north florida for thanksgiving so she stayed in my room so i couldn't leave ahh well i catched up on sleep!! and that leaves me to tonight, ambers coming to pick me up and then we're going over to "j" house...but yeah she'll be here anytime now so i gotta go get ready...i'll let u know how tonight goes....lol...laterness
